<div class="w-full bg-bunker-500 px-8 lg:px-20 py-40 flex flex-col xl:flex-row justify-center">
   <div>
      <h3 class="text-coral-500 font-semibold text-5xl w-full md:max-w-md">Bettering the World Around Us</h3>
      <p class="text-bunker-300 max-w-sm">Our core value of <b>Bettering the World Around Us</b> assumes a holistic approach to
         sustainability. Sustainability
         influences how we develop products as well as how we view our responsibility for the world around us. We give
         back to those less fortunate and are mindful of our precious earth. A few of the things we do is planting trees
         to offset our carbont footprint - over 5,400 trees to date. We use solar energy in our Irvine headquarters and
         our warehouse in North Carolina.</p>
   </div>
